text: Raszków () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Radków, within Kłodzko County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south-western Poland. It lies approximately east of Radków, north-west of Kłodzko, and south-west of the regional capital Wrocław. {| align="left" style="clear:left;float:left" |- |Saints Peter and Paul church |Field crops in Raszków |} ==References== Category:Villages in Kłodzko County
